      "time": "00:06:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I just wanted you to be healthy and happy every day.",
      "zh": "我只希望你每天健康快樂。",
      "ja": "私はただあなたが毎日健康で幸せでいてほしいだけです。",
      "time": "00:06:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And an inner voice in me right at that moment told my mom that,",
      "zh": "那一刻我內心的聲音告訴媽媽，",
