    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "oh, my home, no, mom, I still want to keep working",
      "zh": "喔，媽媽，不，我還想繼續工作，",
      "ja": "ああ、母さん、いいえ、私はまだ働き続けたいです。",
      "time": "00:06:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "because I know that I can fix it.",
      "zh": "因為我知道我可以改進。",
