      "time": "00:07:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "because everyone is different.",
      "zh": "因為每個人都不同。",
      "ja": "なぜなら、みんな違うからです。",
      "time": "00:07:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And the lesson I learned hard way from this big event",
