      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "as a TV host at BTV7.",
      "zh": "作為BTV7的電視主持人。",
      "ja": "BTV7のテレビ司会者として。",
      "time": "00:08:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I still, the full-time student at my diplomatic academy",
