      "ja": "私は外交アカデミーのフルタイム学生でもあります。",
      "time": "00:08:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "of Vietnam.",
      "zh": "越南外交學院。",
      "ja": "ベトナムの。",
      "time": "00:08:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And regarding my voice, as a lot of audience complained",
