      "time": "00:09:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "the producer and the director of the show",
      "zh": "節目的製作人和導演，",
      "ja": "番組のプロデューサーとディレクターが、",
      "time": "00:09:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "that I hosted uploaded a podcast that had me hosting",
