    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It was happening.",
      "zh": "事情正在發生。",
      "ja": "それが起こっていました。",
      "time": "00:10:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Am I making you angry?",
      "zh": "我讓你生氣了嗎？",
      "ja": "私はあなたを怒らせていますか？",
      "time": "00:10:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I didn't know what was happening back then.",
