    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I was so stupid.",
      "zh": "我真笨。",
      "ja": "私はとても愚かでした。",
      "time": "00:10:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It was not until when I talked to people,",
