      "time": "00:15:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "because the cloud rains when it's heavy too.",
      "zh": "因為雲層厚重時也會下雨。",
      "ja": "雲が重い時に雨が降るように。",
      "time": "00:15:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So it's really okay. It's totally normal.",
      "zh": "所以真的沒關係，這很正常。",
      "ja": "だから本当に大丈夫です。完全に普通のことです。",
      "time": "00:15:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You don't have to try to become anyone else.",
      "zh": "你不必試著成為別人。",
      "ja": "誰か他の人になろうとする必要はありません。",
      "time": "00:15:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You just be you.",
      "zh": "你只要做你自己。",
      "ja": "ただ自分らしくいればいいのです。",
      "time": "00:15:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And being you, being authentic, being an individual,",
