      "time": "00:15:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I know that some of you here,",
      "zh": "我知道在座的你們中有些人，",
      "ja": "ここにいる皆さんの中には、",
      "time": "00:15:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "every single one of you here,",
