      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "which was pretty expensive back then.",
      "zh": "當時費用相當昂貴。",
      "ja": "当時はかなり高価でした。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And then I passed the contest, which meant that I got direct offers",
